SEARCH
Package it.unipv.ingsfw.JavaBeats.dao

Interface ISearchDAO

All Known Implementing Classes:
SearchDAO
public interface ISearchDAO
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing operations related to the IJBResearchable entity in the database. This interface provides methods to search for IJBResearchable items with a search field.

  • Method Details

    • search

      ArrayList<IJBResearchable> search(String field, JBProfile activeProfile) throws AccountNotFoundException
      Retrieves the complete information regarding all IJBResearchable items that match the search field. Note that it will return a result specific for the user requesting it.
      Parameters:
      field - search field as a String
      activeProfile - current active profile
      Returns:
      results of the search organized in an ArrayList of IJBResearchable
      Throws:
      AccountNotFoundException - if active profile is not found in the database

    • search

      ArrayList<IJBResearchable> search(String field, JBProfile activeProfile, EJBENTITY mode) throws AccountNotFoundException
      Retrieves the complete information of a specific IJBResearchable JavaBeats entity that match the search field. Note that it will return a result specific for the user requesting it.
      Parameters:
      field - search field as a String
      activeProfile - current active profile
      mode - JavaBeats entity to search for
      Returns:
      results of the search organized in an ArrayList of IJBResearchable
      Throws:
      AccountNotFoundException - if active profile is not found in the database
